{"tid":1287873,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"MAMAMOO 頌樂帶埋奶奶黎香港","createTime":"2019-07-05T11:30:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-06T09:40:45.000Z","uid":74065,"like":29,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"8b4fe9ec9351ec99784b457208b702f3f397e489","tid":1287873,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T11:30:18.000Z","msg":"南韓人氣女團MAMAMOO不只形象灑脫、不做作，穿著也很大膽，成員華莎曾多次因火辣的服裝登上版面。她們5日為了行程準備飛往海外，隊長頌樂大展前凸後翹好身材，胸前只有綁起蝴蝶結，露出纖腰、事業線，性感的穿著立刻成為全場焦點。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4215/d4215028.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4215%2Fd4215028.jpg&h=17f4d49f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲頌樂5日現身機場超辣！（圖／翻攝自Mydaily）<br />\n<br />\n頌樂身材雖嬌小、纖瘦，但其實很有料，她5日與成員一齊現身機場，天氣炎熱，她也穿得很火辣，僅穿著單薄的絲綢材質褐色上衣，將衣服綁起蝴蝶結，胸前深V的造型，上露事業線、下露纖腰，機場時尚的穿著相當性感，令歌迷噴鼻血大喊「不給人活」、「太辣囉」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4215/d4215027.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4215%2Fd4215027.jpg&h=ced4c633&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲頌樂上露、下露現身機場。（圖／翻攝自Newsen）<br />\n<br />\nMAMAMOO可性感可率性，不只華莎勇於嘗試各種穿著，頌樂近來也越穿越火辣，展現性感好身材，令粉絲大飽眼福。MAMAMOO此趟行程是為香港「SBS Super Concert IN HONGKONG」。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0veCdAAmhYQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D0veCdAAmhYQ&d=dy0aigSTvaZIWgiFf%2BaM%2BEn12mAFq1syGW6OSBl8LUM%3D&h=1097f4ef\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0veCdAAmhYQ</a>"},{"pid":"e281161f8c381f46a9354fc1feeed6e0cb88bd4e","tid":1287873,"uid":251836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T11:30:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20e0ba33699bb0981d4a53b080adbbd0a4903cfb","tid":1287873,"uid":208486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T11:31:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45566e36cb9ea21bbc5b5210e898178adf97df2b","tid":1287873,"uid":138138,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T11:31:43.000Z","msg":"玟保守同SOLAR好對比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64b0db914eb28e20504b2f0b74e11c61c7c88b67","tid":1287873,"uid":46435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T11:34:25.000Z","msg":"真係好能正.."},{"pid":"1172be23bc40cd5b30fd19ed2490b2e5cc11c3f0","tid":1287873,"uid":213300,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T11:37:06.000Z","msg":"媽木是最正的<br />\n沒有之一<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e4b30522b702660e3d59d61aa5c50d31680a02d","tid":1287873,"uid":190258,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T11:37:48.000Z","msg":"衝上去解開佢..."},{"pid":"53e297e6ae105f2bfec86a3e3be0c8e73c5e1e34","tid":1287873,"uid":117802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3e4b30522b702660e3d59d61aa5c50d31680a02d","tid":1287873,"uid":190258,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T11:37:48.000Z","msg":"衝上去解開佢..."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T11:38:46.000Z","msg":"咪痴線啦"},{"pid":"7cdb8a84fb022e62a379434ef3be4e3878e5ef30","tid":1287873,"uid":74065,"like":1,"dislike":9,"score":-8,"quote":{"pid":"3e4b30522b702660e3d59d61aa5c50d31680a02d","tid":1287873,"uid":190258,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T11:37:48.000Z","msg":"衝上去解開佢..."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T11:38:52.000Z","msg":"會變成咁<br />\n<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/onepiece/images/6/6d/Monkey_D._Luffy_Anime_Post_Timeskip_Infobox.png/revision/latest?cb=20190124235416\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http